    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Karlo Balla</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"http://odsek.medijskestudije.org/arhiva/karlo-bala-mast-strucni-saradnik.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/5d/KarloBalla.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:KarloBalla.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Karlo Balla <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Karlo Balla</b>, (Karlo Balla Jr., Karlo Bala Jr.)<br />\na Serbian computer scientist and assistant professor at Department of Media Studies, Faculty of Philosophy, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Novi_Sad\">University of Novi Sad</a>, where he already obtained his Diploma and Master's degrees in CS in 2004 and 2010 respectively.\nHis research interests include <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Combinatorial_optimization\">combinatorial optimization</a>, <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logistics\">logistics</a>, <a href=\"/Data\" title=\"Data\">data structures</a> and <a href=\"/Algorithms\" title=\"Algorithms\">algorithms</a>, and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Educational_technology\">E-learning</a>.\nAs a chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, he is further interested in chess programming, also working on an own, private engine <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Bala</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Brcanov:Dejan\">Dejan Brcanov</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Gvozdenovic:Nebojsa\">Nebojsa Gvozdenovic</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>Solving Vehicle Routing Problems via Single Generic Transformation Approach</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.econbiz.de/events/event/2nd-logistics-international-conference-logic-2015/10010464439\">LOGIC 2015</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://logic.sf.bg.ac.rs/wp-content/uploads/Papers/LOGIC2015/ID-7.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/r/Radonjic:Aleksandar\">Aleksandar Radonjic</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Bala</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/v/Vujicic:Vladimir\">Vladimir Vujicic</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7565793\">Integer codes correcting double asymmetric errors</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://digital-library.theiet.org/content/journals/iet-com\">IET Communications</a>, Vol. 10, No. 14</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Bala</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Brcanov:Dejan\">Dejan Brcanov</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/g/Gvozdenovic:Nebojsa\">Nebojsa Gvozdenovic</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10100-016-0463-6\">Two-echelon location routing synchronized with production schedules and time windows</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/journal/10100\">CEJOR</a>, Vol. 25, No. 3</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=467092\">Rybka is not perfect! It doesn't see mate in 4!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Bala</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 05, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=484092\">Re: Is the Sicilian Kan refuted?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Bala</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 02, 2006</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?start=0&amp;t=15505&amp;start=10\">Re: fail high handling with transposition tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 03, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=17790&amp;start=4\">Re: Is it time for another new move generator?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 11, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Table-driven_Move_Generation\" title=\"Table-driven Move Generation\">Table-driven Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18930\">Strange behavior</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?start=0&amp;t=25979&amp;start=10\">Re: Hyperbola Quiesscene: hardly any improvement</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Fill_Algorithms\" title=\"Fill Algorithms\">Fill Algorithms</a>, <a href=\"/Hyperbola_Quintessence\" title=\"Hyperbola Quintessence\">Hyperbola Quintessence</a>, <a href=\"/Kogge-Stone_Algorithm\" title=\"Kogge-Stone Algorithm\">Kogge-Stone Algorithm</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Prefix_Algorithms\" title=\"Parallel Prefix Algorithms\">Parallel Prefix Algorithms</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29873&amp;start=25\">Re: Null-moves and zugzwang</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 28, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Zugzwang\" title=\"Zugzwang\">Zugzwang</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39481\">TT behavior</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 25, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=490652&amp;t=45846\">Re: Move Tables - explain as if I'm five</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 05, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Table-driven_Move_Generation\" title=\"Table-driven Move Generation\">Table-driven Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=490672&amp;t=45846\">Re: Move Tables - explain as if I'm five</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 05, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Belzebub#Repetitions\" title=\"Belzebub\">Repetitions in Belzebub</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57560&amp;start=14\">Re: Interesting ideas</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 09, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/B*\" title=\"B*\">B*</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=BPIP-DFISA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"BPIP-DFISA (page does not exist)\">BPIP-DFISA</a>, <a href=\"/Monte-Carlo_Tree_Search\" title=\"Monte-Carlo Tree Search\">Monte-Carlo Tree Search</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63126&amp;start=40\">Re: PieceLists&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 17, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Table-driven_Move_Generation\" title=\"Table-driven Move Generation\">Table-driven Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67300\">Leela on more then one GPU?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 01, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69035&amp;start=8\">Re: Particle Swarm Optimization Code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=SU3x7g4AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Karlo Balla - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/karlo.bala\">Karlo Balla | Facebook</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://odsek.medijskestudije.org/arhiva/karlo-bala-mast-strucni-saradnik.html\">Karlo Bala, asistent – Odsek za medijske studije</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=924890\">Bala, Karlo FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.365chess.com/players/Karlo_Bala\">Karlo Bala chess games - 365Chess.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Karlo_Balla&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://odsek.medijskestudije.org/arhiva/karlo-bala-mast-strucni-saradnik.html\">Karlo Bala, asistent – Odsek za medijske studije</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=924890\">Bala, Karlo FIDE Chess Profile</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39481\">TT behavior</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Karlo Balla</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 25, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp1.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Bala:Karlo\">dblp: Karlo Bala</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Ronald_L._Rivest\" title=\"Ronald L. Rivest\">Ronald L. Rivest</a> (<b>1987</b>). <i>Game Tree Searching by Min/Max Approximation</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_(journal)\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 34, 1, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://people.csail.mit.edu/rivest/Rivest-GameTreeSearchingByMinMaxApproximation.pdf\">pdf 1995</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Eric_B._Baum\" title=\"Eric B. Baum\">Eric B. Baum</a>, <a href=\"/Warren_D._Smith\" title=\"Warren D. Smith\">Warren D. Smith</a> (<b>1995</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Best-Play-for-Imperfect-Players-and-Game-Tree-part-Baum-Warren/5838432c92c8905c7066962400c55ddc8803f11a\">Best Play for Imperfect Players and Game Tree Search</a></i>. Part I - theory, with pseudocode appendix by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Charles_Garrett&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Charles Garrett (page does not exist)\">Charles Garrett</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Yan_Radovilsky\" title=\"Yan Radovilsky\">Yan Radovilsky</a>, <a href=\"/Solomon_Eyal_Shimony\" title=\"Solomon Eyal Shimony\">Solomon Eyal Shimony</a>  (<b>2004</b>). <i>Generalized Model for Rational Game Tree Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.cs.bgu.ac.il/~yanr/Publications/smc04.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301044949\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 129/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 274/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key os